00:00:59.920 --> 00:01:05.240
of a beautiful woman is
unquestionably the most poetical

00:01:05.240 --> 00:01:07.270
topic in the world.

00:01:07.270 --> 00:01:11.630
In her new book, Messud
says, "not to us."

00:01:11.630 --> 00:01:13.510
I give you Claire Messud.

00:01:13.510 --> 00:01:22.810
