00:03:17.740 --> 00:03:21.420
if you're not familiar with
his work, go out and grab it.

00:03:21.420 --> 00:03:23.430
He's one of the most
exhilarating writers.

00:03:23.430 --> 00:03:25.010
Every book is a new adventure.

00:03:25.010 --> 00:03:28.430
Each book is a completely imagined
world and really different.

00:03:28.430 --> 00:03:33.090
And he has said, if it doesn't
seem impossible, why bother trying?

00:03:33.090 --> 00:03:35.960
And I really take that to heart.

00:03:35.960 --> 00:03:40.380 position:56%
