to write an archetypal story

00:04:42.350 --> 00:04:43.710
in a different way.

00:04:43.710 --> 00:04:46.430
So I wanted it almost-- I
wanted it to be, if you will,

00:04:46.430 --> 00:04:51.230
a fable of American
girls' adolescence.

00:04:51.230 --> 00:04:57.220
In that sense, the account of an
almost universal experience, right,

00:04:57.220 --> 00:05:00.590
a distillation of an experience
