of hold it up and ask questions

00:05:19.020 --> 00:05:21.780
about the stories that
we think we know.

00:05:21.780 --> 00:05:26.830
I think that somewhere along the
line, and of course being me,

00:05:26.830 --> 00:05:29.180 position:56%
I cannot remember where, which seems

00:05:29.180 --> 00:05:34.440
in this internet age an
all too common problem.

00:05:34.440 --> 00:05:35.910
I read it somewhere.

00:05:35.910 --> 00:05:37.930
There is a source somewhere.

00:05:37.930 --> 00:05:40.350
But darned if I know.

00:05:40.350 --> 00:05:47.000
But I read, when I was working on
