00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:09.110
whether resee them on TV,
whether they're in the news,

00:08:09.110 --> 00:08:12.120
whether they're told in our
community or by our friends.

00:08:12.120 --> 00:08:14.690
All those stories,
we internalize them.

00:08:14.690 --> 00:08:17.800
We may forget them, but we distill
them and they're part of us.

00:08:17.800 --> 00:08:20.630
And when we approach a narrative,

00:08:20.630 --> 00:08:23.030
we bring all of that
experience to bear.

00:08:23.030 --> 00:08:26.470
And often, we think, I
already know this story.

00:08:26.470 --> 00:08:30.850
And so part of what, part of--

00:08:30.850 --> 00:08:32.950
there are lots of ways in
