00:08:45.590 --> 00:08:51.250
It's the symbiotic back and forth
in between what we all already know

00:08:51.250 --> 00:08:56.200
from the stories we've internalized
and then the stories that we tell

00:08:56.200 --> 00:09:00.100
with that knowledge in mind.

00:09:00.100 --> 00:09:03.850
And so for me, this
story is obviously

00:09:03.850 --> 00:09:08.460
on some level very simply the
story about two girls going

00:09:08.460 --> 00:09:12.960
through adolescence from
the ages of 12 to 15,

00:09:12.960 --> 00:09:17.390
